SchemaItem.Name: Daktela_SendSMS
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" xmlns:string="http://exslt.org/strings" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date string">
<xsl:param name="text"/> <xsl:param name="phoneNumber"/> <xsl:param name="trackingId"/>
<xsl:template match="/"> <xsl:variable name="crlf" select="'
'"/> <xsl:variable name="message" select="translate(AS:Translate(AS:GetConstant('Daktela_SMS_CharacterTranslation'), $text), $crlf, ' ')"/>
<xsl:variable name="sms" select="AS:HttpRequest(concat( 'https://api.daktela.com/api/3.1/SendSMS/xml?number=', string:replace(translate($phoneNumber, ' ', ''), '+', '00'), AS:iif(contains($message, '@'), '&unicode=yes', ''), '&message=', $message, '&confirmation=yes&access_token=', AS:GetConstant('Daktela_API_Token') ))"/>
<xsl:variable name="smsXml" select="AS:ToXml($sms)"/>
<xsl:if test="string($smsXml/api/error)"> <xsl:message terminate="yes"><xsl:value-of select="concat('Selhalo odeslání SMS na číslo ', $phoneNumber, '. Chyba: ', $smsXml/api/error)"/></xsl:message> </xsl:if> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
